reviewText: Added this to my collection of Lionel Nations DVD.  Like it very much.
I enjoy all the TM productions. This is on par with the others. Enjoyable, educational and full of ideas for my own toy train railroad. Recommend to others who enjoy the hobby.
I Have Lionel Nation 1,2, and 3 so I bought thistocomplete my collection - It is very good.  It shows some vintage lionelaswell as modern trains. It was well worth the money.
